@@ TOP section — Phase 4 migration of SectionTop.astro
@@ Indentation is not implicit: every leading space below is typed on purpose.
@@ All 7 cards share the same DATA DIVISION/WORKING-STORAGE SECTION/01 header;
@@ only the 05 group name and the two 10-level VALUE strings vary per card.
@@ No {{cycle}} tag is used - the field-cycling animation this data once fed
@@ was removed (see CLAUDE.md's SectionTop history); every card here is just
@@ static text, same as every other migrated section.
